meico.mpm.elements.styles

Class TempoStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • meico.xml.AbstractXmlSubtree
      • meico.mpm.elements.styles.GenericStyle<TempoDef>
        • meico.mpm.elements.styles.TempoStyle

  • public class TempoStyle
extends GenericStyle<TempoDef>
    This class interfaces tempo style definitions. Basically, these define a string (such as "Allegro", "fast", "as slow as possible") and assotiate it with an instance of TempoDef.
    Author:
    Axel Berndt
